    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Domnus <persName
                            key="#Princeps" ref="#people/303">Arichis</persName> piissimus atque
                        excellentissimus <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs> gentis Langubardorum,
                        divino premonitus nutu, offero in <orgName key="#Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/85"><rs key="#Churches">ęcclesia</rs> Sancte
                            Sophie</orgName> quam a fundamentis edificavi, pro redemptione anime mee
                        seu pro salvatione gentis nostre et patrię, <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesia</rs> quod edificata est in [*********] Sancti Nicandri et
                        Sancti Felicii in <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Actio" ref="#places/2836"
                                ><geogName ref="#estates/3430" key="#Landed_possessions #Actio"><rs
                                    key="#Actio">acto</rs> Sipontino</geogName></placeName>, locum
                        ubi Bubata dicitur, cum integre <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >territorie</rs> sacri nostro palatio per hos <rs key="#Fines"
                            >fines</rs>: a Frassino per <rs key="#Shores">ripa</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Rivers" ref="#places/3448">Cerbarum</placeName> usque in via
                        puplica et per ipsa via usque in finem de casale Boccellati et deinde in
                        carrara subtus eadem <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3454"><rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> Sancti
                            Felici et Sancti Nicandri</orgName>, deinde in mandra Ballata et usque
                        in <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio</rs> Cerbarum et exiente usque in badu de Mazu
                        Cani; et omnia in integro in prephato monasterio Sancte Sophie offerui
                        possidendum. Quod vero preceptus oblationis ex iussione et dictatus nominate
                        potestatis scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary" ref="#people/3410"
                            >Lupoald</persName> notarius. Actus <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventus</placeName> in filicissimo palatio in anno
                        septimo decimo, mensi novembrio per indictione tertia decima.
                        Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
